name: K/DA POP/STARS
description:
I am not a League player, but I don't know how many times I watched that Popstars video. 

Big props to Riot Games for the skins, and Fortiche Prod for giving them so much life! 

Whenever I see works like this, I wish I could animate :( I can't, so I drew in the air for about 30 hours instead. 

I probably won't be posting anything new for the rest of the year so happy holidays to you all <3 

Thank you for the support! 

PS: Apologies if I got some details wrong!
